      </Run>
            </Span>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph FontFamily="Times New Roman" FontSize="14.666666666666666" TextIndent="24" Margin="0,0,0,7.47">
            <Span>
                <Run>The plan of action and milestones is a key document in the security program. 
                The plan of action and milestones updates is based on the findings from security control assessments, 
                security impact analyses, and continuous monitoring activities. </Run>
            </Span>
        </Paragraph>
